    dc:description "Figure 9. Uvariodendron anisatum Verdc A entire specimen sheet with young branch and leaves B fruit with four monocarps (one detached) C stamen, side view D flower and pedicel attached to bark clump, semi-bottom view E detail of flower, bottom view F detail of flower showing sepals, one outer petal removed, semi-top view. A Verdcourt 406 B Verdcourt 674 D-F Faden 74 / 886. Photos Leo-Paul Dagallier." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/909868" ;
